<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <%- include('./partials/head') %> 
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <%- include('./partials/header') %> 
      <section class="help">
        <h1><%= title %> <img class="rb-logo" src="/images/logo192.png" alt=""> > Help</h1>
        <hr>
        <p>Here you will find all the information to use this API</p>
        <article>

        </article>
        <article id="register">
          <h3>Register:</h3>
          <p>This route reponses to form submit to <code>POST</code> <a href="#register">/api/register</a></p>
          <p>Accepts:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><code>firstName: valid-name</code></li>
            <li><code>lastName: valid-lastName</code></li>
            <li><code>email: valid-email ( *Is an email, *Is not in the current db) </code></li>
            <li><code>password: valid-password ( * More than 5 characters)(Password will be encrypted automatically) </code></li>
            <li><code>birth: valid-date</code></li>
          </ul>
          <p>Values that will be added by default:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><code>id: auto-generated</code></li>
            <li><code>accountData: { "available" : defaultBalance, "transactions" : {} }</code></li>
          </ul>
          <p>Expected response:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Success: <code>{ "msg" : "User created"}</code></li>
            <li>Unsuccess: <code>{ "list of error" : "detail of error." }</code></li>
          </ul>
        </article>
        <hr>
        <article id="login">
          <h3>Login:</h3>
          <p>This route reponses to <code>POST</code> <a href="#login">/api/login</a></p>
          <p>Accepts:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><code>email: valid-email ( *Email is in the current db )</code></li>
            <li><code>password: valid-password ( * password matches with the one in the db)</code></li>
          </ul>
          <p>Expected response:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Success: <code>{ "message" : "User Logged In"}</code></li>
            <li>Unsuccess: <code>{ "message" : "User or password incorrect." }</code></li>
          </ul>
        </article>
        <hr>

        <article id="account">
          <h3>Account:</h3>
          <p>This route reponses to <code>GET</code> <a href="#account">/api/account</a></p>
          <p>Expected response:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>In active session: <code>{ "Account Logged: name + lastName + email | Available: balance"}</code></li>
            <li>None active session: <code>{ "Please login to access your information." }</code></li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </section>
      <%- include('./partials/footer') %> 
    </div>
  </body>
</html>